Title: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to "Trooper Edward J. Sweeney"
Summary: Dedicates a portion of the state highway system to "Trooper Edward J. Sweeney" in the town of Hempstead, county of Nassau.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to dedicating a portion of the state highway system to "Trooper Edward J. Sweeney"
